{"tid":2018372,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中小學英文從未合格 依家考返IELTS overall 6","createTime":"2020-05-15T14:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T03:59:05.000Z","uid":337039,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cf1649a87df9dcd8fdbe140a18008333cfb66967","tid":2018372,"uid":337039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"首先我知道6依個數字係香港唔高, 甚至可能係低<br />\n但係對我黎講, 依個係一個好大既進步<br />\n<br />\n我自己中小學從來冇認真上過任何一堂英文堂<br />\n導致考試就算我認真考, 都係只有10-30分<br />\n不但成日唔返學之後仲退左學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係最近從新開始學習英文<br />\n用左1年左右, 總算考到6分 <br />\n<br />\n我打依篇文最主要係想同大家分享, 做任何野都唔好一開始就認為自己做唔到<br />\n我自己唔認真上堂就係因為自己認為自己唔會學得識英文<br />\n但係當你開始嘗試, 你會發現其實係你自己比左限制自己<br />\n甚至你會覺得你當初討厭既野, 其實都幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9634b11e1a3233e3d028fcddaeb171dac3fc348","tid":2018372,"uid":148002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"6都算係咁，已經好過好多人"},{"pid":"085ee70f469ca1dcd9d9e0e427b5e1237ca017c8","tid":2018372,"uid":134438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:42:34.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"47520d14ba3a92324a0a59dbe26b5a2431b7b254","tid":2018372,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:43:15.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"3d43031b8e4f44665ab3eeeac3089762d316893b","tid":2018372,"uid":126510,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:43:45.000Z","msg":"有啲好奇樓主細分係點<br />\n我估應該係Reading最高分？<br />\n<br />\n香港平均係6.53 (2018 data)<br />\n樓主再接再厲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgjYBoS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgjYBoS.jpg&h=9cefde9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b260e2c314c140ed8ce97c10e2507e07dbdece8","tid":2018372,"uid":336645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0